{"tid":725641,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩睇完波 左邊春袋冤冤痛","createTime":"2018-07-01T19:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T14:52:12.000Z","uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a5d037a32e68afae48e837033673da938a93c0","tid":725641,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:21:01.000Z","msg":"頭先睇完頭場諗住訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一訓無啦啦左邊粒丸痛<br />\n痛症半信鐘左右 又唔係好痛 可以忍受到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n本身諗住去睇急症<br />\n出去之前諗住洗一洗條丁<br />\n浸一浸熱水 而家開始無乜點痛 有少少餘韻<br />\n有無巴打知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef14c8a1ae1affc76b8ca6b6d7c4bab9a400c66","tid":725641,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:24:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f7ff7721c92af865ab9263cb1bad708455a8646","tid":725641,"uid":106468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"精索靜脈曲張<br />\n多數都係左邊出事"},{"pid":"6d098596802660d37706e3843b951e41fef9dbf3","tid":725641,"uid":13474,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:32:23.000Z","msg":"下世小心D喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37eb1a7970d49b6adab7748eb82087c707f6cdee","tid":725641,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f7ff7721c92af865ab9263cb1bad708455a8646","tid":725641,"uid":106468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:30:47.000Z","msg":"精索靜脈曲張<br />\n多數都係左邊出事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:34:11.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n因為多數人用右手打飛機"},{"pid":"22713eeeffb53fa20e630b94eeee39b894be74df","tid":725641,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:38:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家無痛 仲洗唔洗去急症<br />\n上網見人扭蛋 好撚恐怖<br />\n頭先痛個時