ote":{"pid":"4cc0c0814eff8e1a303591da5b0f40d97ed42b12","tid":725641,"uid":62167,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:49:36.000Z","msg":"唔痛=粒蛋已經壞死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:51:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好嚇我呀大佬"},{"pid":"f3989d4a95c08ba552be70176a8053b415e1039c","tid":725641,"uid":128160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-01T19:52:37.000Z","msg":"唔舒服仲上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff7e4dc031c28042bf6e8684d6b861801b4e391","tid":725641,"uid":192765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"幫個春袋按摩一下<br />\n等佢血液循環<br />\n再感到痛楚就切"},{"pid":"d139dc01c34b62e30d3c5582b38e23d76feabd5a","tid":725641,"uid":66825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T04:48:49.000Z","msg":"唔緊要你還有右邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c2780d10266d1f1881747aa8c9c7b5572292ee5","tid":725641,"uid":18569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:38:42.000Z","msg":"單春姐，唔緊要"},{"pid":"368bab430b5b89f4adde90592b8d81d93e9a620b","tid":725641,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T07:43:09.000Z","msg":"去睇醫生 有機會發炎 無咩既 俾醫生摸下 開藥俾你食咁姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd6db471aad913cfa0fe3c141a3065c38a9ee6ea","tid":725641,"uid":2446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T08:00:35.000Z","msg":"丸同袋兩回事"},{"pid":"2eda7ca881abaca50d83f6f90cbc6f818878bcf0","tid":725641,"uid":46083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"之前我試過兩粒蛋打結，初頭情況同你一樣，後尾就痛撚到起地下碌call唔到白車，如果屋企人唔係到嘅話就會小咁兩粒蛋，你唔怕可以唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44ede1652b449818aa23bfde87b1a65f90912113","tid":725641,"uid":44828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2eda7ca881abaca50d83f6f90cbc6f818878bcf0","tid":725641,"uid":46083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"之前我試過兩粒蛋打結，初頭情況同你一樣，後尾就痛撚到起地下碌call唔到白車，如果屋企人唔係到嘅話就會小咁兩粒蛋，你唔怕可以唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁撚大獲 我自己一個住"},{"pid":"aff112bc020b24b0890752d6e6e025b1012f765c","tid":725641,"uid":23719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:40:45.000Z","msg":"搭單問，我又係近排左邊睪丸底好唔舒服，稱唔上痛但總之怪怪地咁，似係有小小痺嘅感覺<br />\n初頭以為因為著得多緊身褲（其實一星期先一次），著緊身褲嗰日仲要痺得好緊要，所以諗住唔著就無事<br />\n呢兩日零零星星都有呢種感覺，間唔時喺左下腹深處都好似有牽扯感覺<br />\n依家間唔時右邊都有少少痺，有無巴打知我老友乜事？（好驚影響生育能力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n利申：上星期一開始出現徵狀，昨日咁啱頭痛眼痛同發燒，聽日諗住睇家庭醫生摸摸底先決定睇唔睇泌尿"},{"pid":"90f6b2f49f1b8bf406388db1494d87d71ba32051","tid":725641,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T13:41:28.000Z","msg":"扭蛋"}]}